data.description: Welcome to this stunning property that offers the perfect blend of elegance and functionality. This home is located in a tranquil neighborhood that provides peace of mind. As you step inside through the impressive 8-ft entry door, you'll immediately notice the airy ambiance created by the 9-ft. ceilings and the abundance of natural light filtering through the double pane windows. The interior features numerous upgrades, including 2-inch faux wood blinds that enhance both privacy and aesthetics. The spacious kitchen is a chef's dream, boasting 42-inch upper cabinets for ample storage, sleek Silestone countertops that exude sophistication, and top-of-the-line Whirlpool appliances, including a range with double ovens and self-cleaning capabilities. The walk-in pantry provides even more convenience for all your culinary needs. Retreat to the primary bedroom, which offers a peaceful sanctuary with its double doors and raised vanities in the en-suite bathroom. Bath 2 showcases a porcelain tub and shower with a tile surround, adding a touch of luxury. A standout feature of the home is a spacious loft area with a closet ideal for a versatile living space or extra storage. Outside, the extended patio is perfect for outdoor entertaining and relaxation, while the front and backyard sprinkler systems ensure lush and vibrant landscaping. The privacy fence adds an extra layer of seclusion to enjoy the outdoor space. Featuring proximity to UTSA, SeaWorld, and Lackland AFB, as well as a part of NISD, this home offers an exceptional location. With its open floor plan, breakfast bar, and loft upstairs, this property seamlessly combines modern design elements with practicality, making it the ideal place to call home. Don't miss the opportunity to make this exceptional property yours. **Sellers are offering $5,000.00 in concessions!
